    "hero": {
      "title": "MAKE YOUR OWN BOUQUET",
      "description": "Enjoy an afternoon of creating, sipping, and socializing in our beautiful flower bar. Whether you're a beginner or have a green thumb, our flower bar is for everyone. Come join us and leave with a beautiful, custom-made bouquet and a heart full of joy.",
