    "testimonials": [
      {
        "photo": "/florals/image-03.jpg",
        "quote": "\"When I say Maritza knows how to carry out a vision.... I MEAN IT!!!! Our wedding day was IDENTICAL to the vision we shared with Maritza while planning. Her floral design took our wedding to the next level and to top it all off, her heart matches the beauty of her gift!\n\nFrom our beautifully curated estate tables to the sweetheart table, ceremony décor and minor details, every guest was in awe....we were in awe! I even cried when she delivered my bouquet because it was EXACTLY what I've imagined my entire life.\n\nWe are so blessed that we were able to experience her God given gift. She made our wedding the dream that it was and we will ALWAYS remember her and her team!\n\nIf you're looking for a floral designer to execute your vision, look no further! Maritza is THE BEST floral designer I've EVER come in contact with!\n\nMaritza, we pray that you continue to operate in your purpose! You have a gift and we are so blessed to have had you!\"",
        "author": "Jillian Curry"
      }
    ],
